timelineItems.text: CHANCE #Rapids96: Keeper Clark just scoops the ball away from the leaping Doyle at the far post. (82) 1-2 #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew SC
timelineItems.text: 83': Colorado makes its final sub as Gabriel Torres enters the match for Marcelo Sarvas. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.desc: Offside, Colorado Rapids. Dillon Serna tries a through ball, but Gabriel Torres is caught offside.
timelineItems.title: OFFSIDE: Gabriel Torres late-game goal gets called back

timelineItems.name: John Bava III
timelineItems.text: What a save by Clark to preserve the lead and boy did he take a shot from Doyle as they were both going for it. Excellent hustle! #CrewSC

timelineItems.name: Massive Report
timelineItems.text: 84’ Clark stays on and #CrewSC see out the danger. Still 2-1 to Columbus.

timelineItems.desc: Attempt missed. Kei Kamara (Columbus Crew SC) right footed shot from the center of the box is close, but misses the top left corner.
timelineItems.title: MISS: Kei Kamara tries a bicycle kick in front of goal, but it goes wide

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: CHANCE #Rapids96: Torres 'scores' but it flagged offside. (85) 1-2 #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Marcus Stephenson
timelineItems.text: OFFSIDE!! 👏👏👏 #COLvCLB #CrewSC

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: Chance #CLB: Irwin saves from Finlay's header and Kamara nearly turns in the rebound. (87) 1-2 #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew SC
timelineItems.text: 87': Kamara responds with a bike from the ground but it's wide! Such skills. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Adam Jardy
timelineItems.text: If Kamara had netted a hat trick on that goal, this would've gone down as an all-time type of night for #CrewSC.

timelineItems.desc: Second yellow card to Axel Sjoberg (Colorado Rapids) for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: RED CARD: Axel Sjoberg gets ejected after receiving a second yellow card

timelineItems.name: John Bava III
timelineItems.text: That would've been quite the cheeky way to get the hat trick if Kamara could've finished that one on the ground. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: MassiveCity
timelineItems.text: .@keikamara is literally about 6 inches away from having 5 goals in this match. Incredible performance. #COLvCLB

timelineItems.desc: Attempt missed. Kevin Doyle (Colorado Rapids) right footed shot from a difficult angle on the left is just a bit too high. Assisted by Vicente Sanchez with a cross following a corner.
timelineItems.title: MISS: Kevin Doyle flicks it just over the crossbar

timelineItems.name: Massive Report
timelineItems.text: 90’ 2-1 #CrewSC lead. Five minutes of stoppage remains.

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew SC
timelineItems.text: 90': Axel Sjöberg is issued a second yellow card, resulting in a red and sending him off the field. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: Red #Rapids96: @SjobergAxel gets a second yellow. (90) 1-2 #COLvCLB

timelineItems.desc: Federico Higuain (Columbus Crew SC) is shown the yellow card for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Federico Higuain called for a handball

timelineItems.name: Massive Report
timelineItems.text: 90’ Sjoberg holds Kamara and gets a second yellow. Was well earned. #Rapids96 down to 10.

timelineItems.name: Adam Jardy
timelineItems.text: #CrewSC was rumored to be set to draft Axel Sjoberg in SuperDraft. Instead, traded pick to Rapids, acquired Chris Klute in process.

timelineItems.desc: Attempt missed. Sam Cronin (Colorado Rapids) left footed shot from very close range is close, but misses to the right.
timelineItems.title: CLEARANCE: Chris Klute kicks away a close almost-equalizer in extra time

timelineItems.name: John Bava III
timelineItems.text: Kei Kamara has been a thorn in the side of Axel Sjöberg all night and that 2nd yellow was the icing on the cake. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: CHANCE #Rapids96: Cronin nearly turns the ball home from close range. (90) 1-2 #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Columbus Crew SC
timelineItems.text: 90'+2': Pipa is issued a yellow card. #CrewSC #COLvCLB

timelineItems.name: Chris Macchi
timelineItems.text: This #COLvCLB match is a battle of GKs wearing fairly old boots. Someone get them some adidas ACE's. #GKsAreFootballersToo

timelineItems.name: Matt Goshert
timelineItems.text: 3 points! #Rapids96 ... Oh wait. No points.

timelineItems.name: Adam Jardy
timelineItems.text: Jack McInerney comes on in the 96th minute (not a typo) and he replaces Federico Higuain. That's interesting. #CrewSC
